Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.12,1:45:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,cô ấy vẫn cứ cảm thấy bất an. {I think he's talking about Rina, hence the usage of she -Rop}{He's talking about Sammy. See Sammy's flashback between ep 3 and 4. --kureshii}
